parachute to safety but was hurt in the fall and died en route to
the hospital, Tavares said.
   The cause of the crash was under investigation.
   The Tucano, a turboprop plane that is lighter and easier to fly
than other training craft, has been sold to Argentina, Paraguay,
Britain and Middle Eastern countries in recent years.
