<TEXT>
   President Bush has directed that U.S. military
forces sent to St. Croix in the aftermath of Hurrican Hugo begin
returning to their home bases, the Pentagon announced Thursday.
   The Army troops, about 1,000 military police from several
different posts, will be brought back from the U.S. Virgin Islands
